column5: Fantastic Newly Remodeled 2 bedroom duplex in Central Austin less than 10 minutes drive to all of the live music and events downtown. University of Texas campus 3 miles away. Circuit of the Americas F1 race track is 15 min away. Everything is Brand New and nothing was overlooked in this Mid Century Modern house. Quartz counter tops, travertine stone floors, new appliances, floor to ceiling vaulted windows, private courtyard and backyard. Quiet neighborhood with shopping and restaurants nearby.
column8: MODERN SUPER TRENDY Central Austin 8 min Downtown
